Text: Thank you. Always a good download. Keep it up! Don't let the small numbers discourage anyone. This is time sensitive material so people don't keep seeding. GO GLENN!

Actually, I've noticed that this stuff generally remains seeded for at least a few weeks. I've also noticed lots of peers downloading from China and Eastern Europe. :)
If you want episodes since June 21 2010, post a comment, and I'll re-seed it.
